data.description: Welcome home to this southern charmer! This quaint 3BR/2BA home has been renovated w/ new paint, SS appliances, quartz countertops & backsplash in the kitchen, and new LVP flooring in all main living areas. The kitchen features an ample amount of cabinet space. Retreat to the great room on those cold nights & warm up to the fireplace in this adorable home. Vaulted ceiling in the great room makes the room feel even more spacious. This home features a split bedroom plan so after a long day you can retreat to your primary bedroom and relax in the on-suite garden tub, soaking in a nice bubble bath. Enjoy the view from the front or rear porch's and enjoy those evening sunsets. The large open lot has plenty of space for entertaining. Sit around the firepit with friends and family and let the memories begin. Large shed in backyard has plenty of space for tools or storage. Great country living with shopping and restaurants nearby - Close proximity to Charlotte but low Union County taxes.
